** Assumptions and methodology: 
- Total ballots cast will be 435 
- Total first-time voters will be 20 and each candidate will receive the same % among them as he received among first-time voters last year 
- Returning # of voters will be 415
327 votes needed for 75% - ((415 * actual % from 2016) + (20 * % among first-time voters last year)) = # of net gained votes needed this year for 75%
